	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />That isn't fake, its just a different (earlier?) PCB version.  Only SMB/DH used the MHROM board, and only SMB/DH has the MH product code on the prg/chr.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


